        How to Prepare for Auction Day: a Brisbane Seller's Checklist
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Auction day itself is only thirty minutes. The preparation that produces a good result takes the week before, and the calm decisions you make on the morning of. Here is the checklist.
      </p>
